(7, 7, 1, 'Quiksilver Surfschool 5/4/3mm wetsuit SS504MG BKW Black', '159.95€', 'The Cypher has been improved with the addition of Dryoprene, a combo of FN Lite Neoprene and Recycled Poly Infused with CoConut Charcoal making it the warmest, fastest drying thermal lining to date. Combined with Hydrolock Seam Seals, a water-block semi dry zipper and flush lock seals on the wrists and ankles, the Cypher will certainly keep you warm in the line up.\r\n\r\nDetails\r\n\r\nThickness: 5/4/3mm\r\n\r\nNeoprene: FN Lite Neoprene\r\n\r\nSeams: Hydrolock Seam Seals\r\n\r\nZipper: Chest Zip\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nProduct F', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/quiksilver/older/Surf+School+3+2MM+L+SL+Steamer+Wetsuit-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:07:43'),
