(12, 12, 1, 'Quiksilver CYPHER hooded 5/4/3mm winter wetsuit', '349.95€', 'Details\r\n\r\nThickness: 5/4/3mm\r\n\r\nNeoprene: FN Lite Neoprene\r\n\r\nSeams: Hydrolock Seam Seals\r\n\r\nZipper: Chest Zip\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nProduct Features\r\n\r\nHydrolock Seam Seal\r\nThermobamboo\r\nFN Lite Neoprene\r\nFlush Lock Seals on wrists and ankles\r\nWater Block Semi Dry Zip\r\nThermal Smoothie Hood\r\nEcto Flex Knee Pads', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/quiksilver/older/q-cypher-654-hdhft-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:14:59'),
(13, 13, 1, 'Quiksilver CYPHER 5.5/5/4/3mm winter wetsuit', '399.95€', 'The Cypher is geared towards the person who wants an ultra lightweight, flexible and warm wetsuit which will perform in the harshest of winter conditions. The fuseflex system is Quiksilvers solution to do away with stitching. Conventional stitching creates less flexibility within a wetsuit, so the Cypher uses a pressure bonded seal on the seams to add even more flex throughout the wetsuit. To add more warmth to the Cypher, Quiksilver has added their Plio Air Chamber neoprene technology to the ch', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/quiksilver/older/Cypher-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:15:08'),
(14, 14, 1, 'Quiksilver Cypher 3.5mm Hood with Dickie and Hft', '49.95€', 'Quiksilver Cypher 3.5mm Hood will keel you nice and toasty on the coldest days.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n\r\nPlio-tech termal air chamber neoprene\r\n	Bio-fleece thermal lining\r\n	DST (Dual seal treatment)\r\n	GBS (Glued and Blind Sitched)', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/quiksilver/older/quiksilver-cypher-full-wetsuit-hood-3.5mm-10590-p-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:15:20'),
(15, 15, 1, 'Quiksilver Cypher 3.5mm Hood', '44.95€', 'Quiksilver Cypher 3.5mm Hood will keel you nice and toasty on the coldest days.\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n\r\nFiber-lite neoprene, super soft and 100% stretch\r\n	Vaporstretch mesh', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/quiksilver/older/ech821ms_cypherhooddickie,v_blk_frt1-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:15:31'),
(16, 16, 1, 'North X-Ride', '599.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST CARVING ABILITIES\r\n	GREAT CONTROL\r\n	MOST COMFORTABLE BOARD\r\nGREAT FOR FLATWATER AND WAVES\r\n	STEP MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	BIAX FIBRE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe X-Ride is one of the most popular boards on the market and is the choise board of riders all over the world. It is designed to be ridden about 3 cm longer than your standard board. The increase in the rocker line helps to make the X-Ride extremely smooth over choppy water. The outline shape is also a little narr', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/xride_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:15:40'),
(17, 17, 1, 'North Woohoo', '899.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nSMALL TO WELL OVERHEAD HIGH WAVES\r\n	BEST SURFBOARD\r\n	NO INSERTS FOR FOOTSTRAPS\r\nPERFECT IN THE POCKET\r\n	SNAPPY TOP TURNS & TIGHT BOTTOM TURNS\r\n	LIGHT TEAM CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Pro Surf is aimed at the rider looking for a more traditional shape, yet still wanting maximum performance. By using a straightforward design approach Sky Solbach has created a finely tuned high performance board aimed to suit the power surfing style of some of our top pro riders when the waves are f', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/wohoo_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:15:48'),
(18, 18, 1, 'North Whip CSC', '899.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nSMALL TO MEDIUM SIZED WAVES & STRAPLESS FREESTYLE\r\n	BEST WAVE FREESTYLE BOARD\r\n	EARLY PLANING\r\nVERY FORGIVING\r\n	FAST BOTTOM TURNS\r\n	CLASSIC CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Whip CSC is the perfect all round surfboard in the Compact Surf Concept range. It is really easy to ride and very forgiving and the rail design combines with the modern outline to cut through chop effortlessly. On the wave it is great for carving smooth arching turns but it will also allow you to ride it aggressive', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/whip_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:15:58'),
(19, 19, 1, 'North Wam', '899.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nALL CONDITIONS BEST ALL-ROUND PERFORMANCE\r\n	HIGH PERFORMANCE ALL-ROUNDER\r\n	EASY TO SURF\r\nDRIVY BOTTOM TURNS & EASY TOP TURNS\r\n	GOOD CONTROL\r\n	CLASSIC CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe WAM has been one of our most popular surfboards for many years, but for 2016 it features a brand new shape. The new board combines a wide squash tail with a broader more high performance nose shape. This effectively increases the overall rail line while increasing the surface area of the board. The benefi', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/wam_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:16:08'),
(20, 20, 1, 'North Wakestyle Bar', '589.00€', ' \r\n\r\nProduct\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\ndeveloped by the Freestyle/Wakestyle Team\r\n	5 lines with low V\r\n	maximum power release delay\r\n	more slack and pop\r\nincludes Hadlow Setup conversion kit\r\n	extra narrow bar width (42 cm)\r\n	single depower line\r\n	bigger chicken loop\r\nThe completely new Wakestyle Bar is based on the Trust Bar but has been fully influenced by the North Kiteboarding Wakestyle/Freestyle Team. They wanted a shorter bar (42cm), a bigger chicken loop, 22m lines, single line depower with a rub', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/Wakestylebar-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:16:19'),
(21, 21, 1, 'NORTH VEGAS', '1,159.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST UNHOOKED PERFORMANCE AND POP UNHOOKED\r\n	RESPONSIVE POWER RELEASE DELAY\r\n	WORKS BEST WITH WAKESTYLEBAR\r\n3 RIDING SETUPS WITH NUMEROUS TRIMMING OPTIONS\r\n	DIRECT & FAST TURNING\r\n	LOADED 5TH LINE\r\nThe benchmark was set many years ago by the Vegas, it is the ultimate freestyle weapon used by our Pro Team to have a resounding effect on the world stage. However, it doubles up as a great kite for ambitious riders too, boosting huge airs and providing great rider feedback! ', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/VEGAS-CC3-01-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:16:29'),
(22, 22, 1, 'NORTH VEGAS', '1,159.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST UNHOOKED PERFORMANCE AND POP UNHOOKED\r\n	RESPONSIVE POWER RELEASE DELAY\r\n	WORKS BEST WITH WAKESTYLEBAR\r\n3 RIDING SETUPS WITH NUMEROUS TRIMMING OPTIONS\r\n	DIRECT & FAST TURNING\r\n	LOADED 5TH LINE\r\nThe benchmark was set many years ago by the Vegas, it is the ultimate freestyle weapon used by our Pro Team to have a resounding effect on the world stage. However, it doubles up as a great kite for ambitious riders too, boosting huge airs and providing great rider feedback! ', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/VEGAS-HADL-01-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:16:40'),
(23, 23, 1, 'NORTH VEGAS', '1,159.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST UNHOOKED PERFORMANCE AND POP UNHOOKED\r\n	RESPONSIVE POWER RELEASE DELAY\r\n	WORKS BEST WITH WAKESTYLEBAR\r\n3 RIDING SETUPS WITH NUMEROUS TRIMMING OPTIONS\r\n	DIRECT & FAST TURNING\r\n	LOADED 5TH LINE\r\nThe benchmark was set many years ago by the Vegas, it is the ultimate freestyle weapon used by our Pro Team to have a resounding effect on the world stage. However, it doubles up as a great kite for ambitious riders too, boosting huge airs and providing great rider feedback! ', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/VEGAS-CC2-011-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:16:49'),
(24, 24, 1, 'North TS Hadlow', '1,049.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST POP IN THE RANGE\r\n	MASSIVE GRIP\r\n	RIDE WITH OR WITHOUT FINS\r\nPERFORMANCE & COMPETITION ORIENTED\r\n	STEP DOUBLE CONCAVE WITH TRAILERFIN\r\n	PREMIUM PERFORMANCE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe choice of our freestyle pro riders, the Team Series is the ultimate board for the competitive rider looking for the ultimate in pop! Used by riders like Reno Romeu and Stefan Spiessberger on the world tour the Team Series wears the badge of excellence like no other. The board is exceedingly sti', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/hadlow_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:02'),
(25, 25, 1, 'North TS', '999.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST POP IN THE RANGE\r\n	MASSIVE GRIP\r\n	RIDE WITH OR WITHOUT FINS\r\nPERFORMANCE & COMPETITION ORIENTED\r\n	STEP DOUBLE CONCAVE WITH TRAILERFIN\r\n	PREMIUM PERFORMANCE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe choice of our freestyle pro riders, the Team Series is the ultimate board for the competitive rider looking for the ultimate in pop! Used by riders like Reno Romeu and Stefan Spiessberger on the world tour the Team Series wears the badge of excellence like no other. The board is exceedingly sti', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/team_series_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:12'),
(26, 26, 1, 'North Spike Textreme', '999.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nULTIMATE LIGHT WIND WEAPON\r\n	EARLIEST PLANING IN THE RANGE\r\n	FANTASTIC UPWIND PERFORMANCE\r\nEXTREMELY LIGHTWEIGHT\r\n	MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	TEXTREME CARBON CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe legendary Spike just got better! By taking the test winning shape of the Spike 153 and utilising the most technological advanced constructions techniques available, the ultimate lightwind freeride board has been created! The Textreme carbon construction makes the board about 20 % lighter than t', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/spiketex_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:22'),
(27, 27, 1, 'North Spike', '629.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nLIGHT WIND WEAPON\r\n	SUPER EARLY PLANING\r\n	FANTASTIC UPWIND PERFORMANCE\r\nGREAT FOR FREERIDE\r\n	MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	BIAX FIBRE CONSTRUCTION\r\nWhen the wind doesn’t blow the Spike is the board you need to get riding! Available in three sizes for various wind conditions and rider weights there is a Spike to suit everyone. The largest board in the range, the 163 offers the best lowend performance and fantastic upwind ability in the lightest of winds and for the heavi', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/spike_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:33'),
(28, 28, 1, 'North Soleil', '599.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nWOMEN SPECIFIC SHAPE\r\n	PERFECT CONTROL\r\n	VERY FORGIVING SHAPE AND FLEX\r\nSMOOTH RIDE\r\n	STEP MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	BIAX FIBRE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe growth in the number of women taking up kitesurfing is phenomenal and the level of riding is going through the roof. The Soleil blends the perfect shape and flex into an amazing board that is specifically designed for female riders. This board delivers a smooth ride in choppy conditions whilst being very forgiving allowing', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/soleil_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:43'),
(29, 29, 1, 'North Select', '999.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nFASTEST BOARD IN THE RANGE\r\n	EARLY PLANING\r\n	EXTREMELY LIGHTWEIGHT\r\nVERY FORGIVING RIDE\r\n	STEP MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	TEXTREME CARBON CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Select sets the standards for freeride performance, incorporating the most advanced construction techniques and technology with a fast, dynamic shape. It is the lightest, fastest and most responsive kiteboard in the range and is perfect for freeride and freestyle riders looking for the ultimate machine to take the', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/select_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:17:53'),
(30, 30, 1, 'NORTH REBEL', '1,089.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\n·         BIGGEST WINDRANGE\r\n\r\n·         BEST HANGTIME AND HIGHEST JUMPS\r\n\r\n·         BEST SHEET & GO POWER DEVELOPMENT\r\n\r\n·         GREAT UPWIND PERFORMANCE\r\n\r\n·         EASY WATER RELAUNCH\r\n\r\n·         LOADED 5TH LINE\r\n\r\nThe new 2016 Rebel is the ultimate kite for huge jumps and massive hangtime! There have been quite a few changes across the range this year to ensure it still delivers the maximum performance across all the sizes. The smaller sizes in the range now fe', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/REBEL-CC2-01-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:18:03'),
