(46, 46, 1, 'NORTH JUICE', '949.00€', ' \r\n\r\nProduct\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nPlayful big kite\r\n	Easy handling\r\nEasy, accessible kite\r\n	Amazing agility\r\nThe second generation of our hugely popular light wind freeride kite, the Juice is ideal for those days on the beach when the wind doesn’t arrive. The kite is available in two sizes, 15m and 18m and is designed around a 3-strut platform to ensure it retains a playful nature in the air, despite the large size! The Juice has amazing upwind performance, even in hardly any wind. Unlike some larg', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/Web_NKB_Juice15-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:20:52'),
(47, 47, 1, 'North Jaime', '679.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nGREAT POP\r\n	EASY TO RIDE\r\n	MOST VERSATILE BOARD\r\nGOOD COMPROMISE BETWEEN PERFORMANCE & COMFORT\r\n	QUATTRO V BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	PREMIUM CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Jaime has been in the North Kiteboarding range for over 10 years now; it’s a fantastic freeride and freestyle machine that perfectly reflects the way our very own Jaime Herraiz rides. It’s the perfect board for riders who are looking for a great freestyle board without the unforgiving stiffness that some of the top end pro', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/jaime_16-600x800.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:21:01'),
(48, 48, 1, 'North Gonzales', '469.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nEASY TO RIDE\r\n	SMOOTH & COMFORTABLE\r\n	SUPER FORGIVING\r\nGREAT UPWIND PERFORMANCE\r\n	MONO CONCAVE BOTTOM CONCEPT\r\n	BIAX FIBRE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Gonzales is one of the easiest to ride kiteboards around. In the smaller sizes it is smooth and forgiving, the larger sizes are perfect for beginners and larger riders. When you are first learning this sport you need a board that will help you to progress and make that progression as fast as possible. The Gonzales does just that wh', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/gonzales_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:21:12'),
(49, 49, 1, 'North Gambler', '739.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nDESIGNED FOR BOOTS\r\n	LARGE ROCKER\r\n	RIDE WITH OR WITHOUT FINS\r\nSTIFF TO MEDIUM FLEX PATTERN\r\n	STEP DOUBLE CONCAVE SLICK BASE\r\n	BIAX FIBRE CONSTRUCTION\r\nThe Gambler is our park and wakestyle board, ridden by guys like Tom Court and Craig Cunningham as well as Colleen Carroll, the multiple winner of the Triple S event. This is the go-to board for our riders looking to hit the park on the kite or cable. Tough, strong and packed with performance it delivers whatever the con', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/gambler_16-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:21:22'),
(50, 50, 1, 'NORTH EVO', '1,159.00€', 'Product\r\n\r\nInformation\r\n\r\nBEST ALL-ROUND KITE IN THE RANGE\r\n	HUGE WIND RANGE\r\n	GREAT HANGTIME & POWERFUL LIFT\r\nGOOD JUMPING ABILITIES\r\n	EXCELLENT UPWIND PERFORMANCE\r\n	HYBRID BETWEEN C-KITE AND DELTA SHAPE\r\nSimply put, the Evo is the all-round maestro from the North Kiteboarding range, guaranteed to get the job done! Any job. We’ve done things different by giving this freeride machine 5 struts instead of 3 struts, because we believe in it. Why? Because with our 5-strut design that has been refine', 'http://www.surfhouse.lt/eshop/image/cache/data/products/North Kiteboarding/EVO-CC1-SEQ-01-600x800.png', '2016-05-02 13:21:31'),
(51, 864, 2, '2013 CrazyFly Sculp 10m2', '500,00€', '2013 CrazyFly Sculp jėgos aitvaras. Pilnas komplektas su pompa, lyšu, baru, kuprine. Būklė labai gera. Šiuo metu yra Vilniaus parduotuvėje.', 'http://www.xpro.lt/471-tm_thickbox_default/2010-cabrinha-switchblade-12m2.jpg', '2016-05-02 13:21:40'),
